headline: SUN PRINCESS NAMED #1 MEGA CRUISE SHIP IN 2025 CONDÉ NAST TRAVELER READERS' CHOICE AWARDS FOR SECOND CONSECUTIVE YEAR
summary: Princess Cruises' stunning Sphere-Class ship, Sun Princess, has once again been recognized as the #1 Mega Cruise Ship in the prestigious Condé Nast Traveler 2025 Readers' Choice Awards. This marks the second consecutive year that Sun Princess has earned the top honor, underscoring her reputation for delivering unforgettable voyages with extraordinary style, innovation, and service.
